data.description: Large family or entertainers dream right here!!  This very nice 3/2 ranch in Southern Belle Estate is a nicely appointed open floor plan with several updates to kitchen, flooring, paint and more. Large living room with fireplace to hang those Christmas stockings on. In ground pool enclosed with privacy fencing and outdoor bathroom/changing area. Large, covered deck great for entertaining right off the living room for guest to flow easily from indoor to outdoor areas. Additional gaming/4th bedroom was added in past years also would make an excellent in-law suite or college age kid’s private area and attached office. Kitchen was remodeled within the last 10 yrs.  Roof was changed after Laura.  A/C approx. 3 yrs. old.  New crown molding in bedroom.  Updated master bath with rolling barn door.  New waterproof LVT floors and new carpet.  Soft close maple cabinets in kitchen with large commercial refrigerator/freezer, dish washer, range and granite counter tops. Includes 3 outdoor bldgs.  Exterior is of cedar and recently fresh paint applied. Inground saltwater pool. Water features off deck. Lots of parking area. This one won’t last long, call me today to view.  Let your imagination run wild with this one. Motivated Sellers!! Seller is offering $5,000 towards Closing Cost or Prepaid Items.
